    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "image_2",
      "label": "Second image"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title_2",
      "label": "Second section title",
      "default": "The Making Process"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "content_2",
      "label": "Second section content",
      "default": "<p>Each piece is carefully crafted by hand, using natural fibers and traditional techniques passed down through generations. We work slowly, paying attention to every stitch, every detail.</p><p>Our process is a meditation—a way to connect with materials, with tradition, and with the stories we want to tell. From selecting the perfect yarn to adding the final touches, every step is done with care and intention.</p><p>We draw inspiration from the gentle transition between seasons—the soft light of late spring, the first warmth of early summer, the quiet beauty of nature awakening.</